title: Gigi Gorgeous
itunes:title: Gigi Gorgeous
description:
Actress, model, author, YouTube legend Gigi Gorgeous is on the pod today and Whitney asks her all the questions other people avoid.  Gigi also talks about being a Trans icon, Mae West and Elvira.  Plus, we have a special guest for ads.  Check out Gigi's podcast QUEERIFIED wherever you get your podcasts.
